article.description: — Pierre Crockrell II scored 17 points as Pacific topped San Francisco 76-69 on Saturday night.
article.headline: Crockrell II lifts Pacific over San Francisco 76-69
article.linkText: Crockrell II lifts Pacific over San Francisco 76-69
article.story: STOCKTON, Calif. -- — Pierre Crockrell II scored 17 points as Pacific topped San Francisco 76-69 on Saturday night. Broc Finstuen and Jeremiah Bailey added 16 points each for the Tigers. Finstuen also had eight rebounds. Jordan Bell had 12 points and eight rebounds for Pacific (9-8, 6-7 West Coast Conference). Jamaree Bouyea had 22 points and 10 rebounds for the Dons (10-13, 4-9), whose losing streak stretched to six games. Julian Rishwain added 21 points. Khalil Shabazz had 15 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
